# cf-todo OpenClaw Skill Configuration Example
#
# Add the following to your ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json:
#
# {
#   "skills": {
#     "entries": {
#       "cf-todo": {
#         "enabled": true,
#         "env": {
#           "CF_TODO_API_URL": "https://todo.example.com",
#           "CF_TODO_API_KEY": "cfk_your_api_key_here"
#         }
#       }
#     }
#   }
# }
#
# How to get an API Key:
# 1. Log in to your cf-todo web UI
# 2. Use the API Key management endpoint:
#    curl -X POST https://todo.example.com/api/v1/keys \
#      -H "Cookie: auth_token=xxx; auth_sig=xxx" \
#      -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#      -d '{"action":"CREATE","name":"openclaw"}'
# 3. Copy the returned key (starts with cfk_) — it's shown only once
